node.text:
Good stuff right here 🙏

This is a dream come true! For a over 3 years I have been using Missile Baits. It all started at a little tackle shop by Cane River and now 3 years later I am getting the opportunity to be able to work with Missile Baits. Thank you to Mr. Derek, Mr. Zach and all the others who have helped me along the way! Y’all are the best and I couldn’t have done this without y’all👊 thank you Mr. John Crews! It’s been great to learn from you and thank you for being willing to help me👊Missile Baits and Missile Jigs are companies who are run by great people who insure quality in each of their products I have a ton of confidence in them! I can name a handful of people in Louisiana who are partners with Missile Baits including Derek Hudnall, Blake Sylvester, Caleb Sumrall, Logan Latuso and Dave Cavell. These guys are all great people who I look up to and it’s so cool that I have an opportunity to represent the same brand they do!
#family #missilebaits #caneriver 
📝@thebasshunter
